# Cold-session freshness sentinel — local state, re-created by pnpm test:cold-session.
# Intentionally untracked: a time-based freshness gate must not live as committed
# state (it misleads agents into attributing failures as "pre-existing"). Enforced
# by `pnpm check:freshness`, not by the regression suite.
tools/learning-loop-mastra/__tests__/legacy-mcp/.cold-session-sentinel.json
